             SlyMail v0.51
             Linux version
This is an offline QWK mail reader that has
a look & feel somewhat similar to Digital
Distortion Message Reader & SlyEdit (mods
for Synchronet). This reader is compatible
with QWKE, color codes from several BBS
software packages, understands Synchronet's
voting system, supports downloading QWK
packets from within the reader (FTP/SSH),
and more.
Release date: 2026-03-25
